{"title":"[CSAPP] Lab2 Phase 1,2 解谜笔记","date":"2017-08-25T02:25:25.000Z","slug":"csapp-lab2-phase-12","tags":["CS","CSAPP","汇编"],"categories":["学习笔记"],"updated":"2018-11-05T04:06:09.171Z","content":"<p>介绍：这是一个“拆弹”游戏，玩家要在反汇编中找到每一关的拆弹密码，一共有6个phases。<br>该Lab的下载地址：<a href=\"http://csapp.cs.cmu.edu/3e/labs.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://csapp.cs.cmu.edu/3e/labs.html</a>。</p>\n<p><strong>警告：本文含有剧透内容，想要玩Lab2的慎看！</strong></p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>先看phase_1<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">0000000000400ee0 &lt;phase_1&gt;:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400ee0:\tsub    $0x8,%rsp</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400ee4:   mov    $0x402400,%esi</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400ee9:\tcallq  401338 &lt;strings_not_equal&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400eee:\ttest   %eax,%eax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400ef0:\tje     400ef7 &lt;phase_1+0x17&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400ef2:\tcallq  40143a &lt;explode_bomb&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400ef7:\tadd    $0x8,%rsp</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400efb:\tretq</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>很短很简单，第2行和第8行是分配和释放栈空间，用来存放局部变量。<br>第3行将地址放到esi，并在第4行调用了函数strings_not_equal。根据寄存器表<br><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2017/08/23/599d6f7191aa0.jpg\" alt=\"reg.jpg\"><br>可以看出这里的调用是<code>strings_not_equal(input, *0x402400)</code><br>然后第5,6行进行了比较，如果字符串相同才不炸。<br>剩下的就简单了，用gdb查一下那个地址存着什么就可以了：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">(gdb) x/s 0x402400</span><br><span class=\"line\">0x402400:       &quot;Border relations with Canada have never been better.&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>输入该字符串过关。</p>\n<p>接下来是phase2<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">0000000000400efc &lt;phase_2&gt;:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400efc:\tpush   %rbp</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400efd:\tpush   %rbx</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400efe:\tsub    $0x28,%rsp</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f02:   mov    %rsp,%rsi    ;rsi=rsp</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f05    callq  40145c &lt;read_six_numbers&gt; ;read 6 numbers into rsp,+4,+8,+12,+16,+20</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f0a:   cmpl   $0x1,(%rsp)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f0e:\tje     400f30 &lt;phase_2+0x34&gt; ;N1==1</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f10:\tcallq  40143a &lt;explode_bomb&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f15:\tjmp    400f30 &lt;phase_2+0x34&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f17:\tmov    -0x4(%rbx),%eax       ;eax=*(rbx-4)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f1a:\tadd    %eax,%eax             ;eax*=2</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f1c:\tcmp    %eax,(%rbx)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f1e:\tje     400f25 &lt;phase_2+0x29&gt; ;if *rbx==eax</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f20:\tcallq  40143a &lt;explode_bomb&gt; ;         |</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f25:   add    $0x4,%rbx             ; rbx+=4</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f29:   cmp    %rbp,%rbx</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f2c:   jne    400f17 &lt;phase_2+0x1b&gt; ;if rbx!=rbp -&gt;400f17</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f2e:   jmp    400f3c &lt;phase_2+0x40&gt; ;else -&gt;400f3c</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f30:   lea    0x4(%rsp),%rbx        ;rbx=rsp+4</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f35:   lea    0x18(%rsp),%rbp       ;rbp=rsp+24</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f3a:   jmp    400f17 &lt;phase_2+0x1b&gt; ;-&gt;400f17</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f3c:   add    $0x28,%rsp</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f40:\tpop    %rbx</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f41:\tpop    %rbp</span><br><span class=\"line\">  400f42:\tretq</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>汇编的含义已经注释在代码里了，一开始用函数read_six_numbers读入了6个数到栈上（那个函数我读了半天(╯‵□′)╯︵┻━┻），然后观察可以看出来中间的部分其实是一个for循环，17-19行是判断语句，20-22行是初始化语句，11-16行则是循环体。转换成伪c代码大约是这样的：<br><figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(rbx=rsp+<span class=\"number\">4</span>,rbp=rsp+<span class=\"number\">24</span>;rbx!=rbp;rbx+=<span class=\"number\">4</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>((*(rbx<span class=\"number\">-4</span>))*<span class=\"number\">2</span>!=*rbx) explode_bomb();</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>结合第8行N1需要等于1的要求，很明显这段代码是要求6个由1开头每次*2的等比数列，即1 2 4 8 16 32。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"[CSAPP] Lab2 Phase 3 解谜笔记","slug":"csapp-lab2-phase-3"},"link":"https://blog.harrynull.tech/post/csapp-lab2-phase-12/","copyright":{"author":"Harry Yu","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.harrynull.tech/post/csapp-lab2-phase-12/\" title=\"[CSAPP] Lab2 Phase 1,2 解谜笔记\">https://blog.harrynull.tech/post/csapp-lab2-phase-12/</a>","published":"August 25, 2017"}}